Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:09.95,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今キミがどこにいたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.96,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}変わるはずないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:20.13,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}心はいつでも 繋がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:24.05,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:26.85,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}忘れずにいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:30.64,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}あの日感じた情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.65,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ふたりで重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:41.07,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}茜色の空 滲んでく夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:49.99,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}上を向いて 歩いていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:44.76,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在被夕陽染紅的坡道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:51.73,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}停下腳步駐足停留的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:58.74,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}總是不經意想起遠去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:05.74,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我試著找回快要迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:09.95,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}無論你現在身處何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}也不會有任何變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:20.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們的心始終緊緊連繫著
